➜北京：国产新冠疫苗“服贸会”首次亮相
http://www.sohu.com/a/416749867_114731	33917
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200906/1a6300107d4d40c4b96612651116b610.jpeg" /></p>
